  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "In spite of the fact that today\nis the last on which the employ\nment agents can pay their licenses\nwithout laying themselves liable to\narrest there are a number who\nhave failed to do so and Major\nr. ID. Gwydir promises to start ar\nrests Monday morning of all those\nwho have failed to pay up. There\nhave been but six licenses taken\nout since the injunction against\nthe city was overruled and there\nare about dozen agents who are\nnow without licenses. There are\nseven holding old licenses which\nhave not expired as yet.\n\n\nThe license fee was raised last\nfall from $50 to $200 per annum\nand this started a fight by the\nagents which resulted in their de-\nfeat in the courts."
    }
  ]
